(INSTALLATION GUIDE) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(App version: v0.1.0-dev) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This guide must be updated after installation, infrastructure, dependency, model,) Tj T*
(database, backup or environment changes.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(OVERVIEW) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This application runs on an Ubuntu 24.04 computer with OpenClaw, PostgreSQL, Ollama) Tj T*
(qwen3:4b, FastAPI, React and background workers.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(REQUIRED SERVICES) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- OpenClaw) Tj T*
(- PostgreSQL) Tj T*
(- Ollama with qwen3:4b) Tj T*
(- FastAPI backend) Tj T*
(- React frontend) Tj T*
(- Background workers) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Use .env.example as the template. Do not commit the real .env file.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Frontend/backend local wiring defaults:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- VITE_BACKEND_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000) Tj T*
(- CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://127.0.0.1:5173,http://localhost:5173) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(POSTGRESQL SETUP) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Use Docker Compose by default because the repository already includes a local-only) Tj T*
(PostgreSQL service. Native PostgreSQL is acceptable later if it is configured with the) Tj T*
(same local-only exposure and environment-variable credential rules.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(PostgreSQL must not be exposed to the internet. The included Compose configuration binds) Tj T*
(PostgreSQL to localhost only:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(text) Tj T*
(127.0.0.1:5432:5432) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Create the real .env from .env.example, then replace placeholder database credentials) Tj T*
(with local secrets. Do not commit .env.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(cp .env.example .env) Tj T*
ET
endstream
endobj
