(EDIT POSTGRES_PASSWORD AND DATABASE_URL IN .ENV ONLY) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Start PostgreSQL with Docker Compose:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(docker compose up -d postgres) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Apply Stage 0 migrations:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(./scripts/db_migrate.sh) Tj T*
(./scripts/db_status.sh) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The migration runner loads .env when present, creates schema_migrations, and applies SQL) Tj T*
(files from database/migrations in filename order. The first migration enables required) Tj T*
(extensions and creates the Stage 0 model-task logging table.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Required extensions for the first migration:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- pgcrypto) Tj T*
(- uuid-ossp) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Stage 0 tables:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- schema_migrations) Tj T*
(- model_task_logs) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Stage 1 wallet tracking tables:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- whale_wallets) Tj T*
(- watchlist) Tj T*
(- wallet_movements) Tj T*
(- agent_alerts) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Stage 2 signal validation tables:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- signal_outcomes) Tj T*
(- token_mappings) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(OLLAMA SETUP) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Ollama must run locally only and the approved V1 local model is qwen3:4b.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Recommended secure defaults for a user-space service:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
ET
endstream
