(bash) Tj T*
(mkdir -p ~/.config/systemd/user) Tj T*
(cat > ~/.config/systemd/user/ollama.service <<'EOF') Tj T*
([Unit]) Tj T*
(Description=Ollama local model server \(user-space\)) Tj T*
(After=network-online.target) Tj T*
(Wants=network-online.target) Tj T*
() Tj T*
([Service]) Tj T*
(Type=simple) Tj T*
(Environment=OLLAMA_HOST=127.0.0.1:11434) Tj T*
(Environment=OLLAMA_MODELS=/home/robot/.ollama/models) Tj T*
(Environment=PATH=/home/robot/.local/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin) Tj T*
(ExecStart=/home/robot/.local/bin/ollama serve) Tj T*
(Restart=on-failure) Tj T*
(RestartSec=5) Tj T*
() Tj T*
([Install]) Tj T*
(WantedBy=default.target) Tj T*
(EOF) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(systemctl --user daemon-reload) Tj T*
(systemctl --user enable --now ollama.service) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The host should have user lingering enabled so the service starts after reboot. Validate) Tj T*
(with:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(loginctl show-user "$USER" -p Linger) Tj T*
(systemctl --user is-enabled ollama.service) Tj T*
(systemctl --user is-active ollama.service) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Install and validate the approved model:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(./scripts/install_ollama_qwen3_4b.sh) Tj T*
(./scripts/test_ollama_qwen3_4b.sh) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The validation scripts fail if Ollama is unreachable, if qwen3:4b is missing, or if) Tj T*
(unexpected local Ollama models are present.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(PAID MODEL SETUP) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Configure ChatGPT as the primary development model and Anthropic as fallback.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
ET
endstream
endobj
