(Stage 0 model routing policy:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Ollama qwen3:4b for low-risk cleanup, classification, extraction, tagging and first-) Tj T*
(pass summaries.) Tj T*
(2. ChatGPT/OpenAI as the primary paid development/reasoning provider.) Tj T*
(3. Anthropic as fallback when ChatGPT/OpenAI token, context, rate or quota limits block) Tj T*
(progress.) Tj T*
(4. Latest suitable paid models only for final higher-risk production/research analysis) Tj T*
(later.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Configure API keys only in the real .env file or host secret manager:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(text) Tj T*
(OPENAI_API_KEY=...) Tj T*
(ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=...) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Do not commit real API keys. Do not expose paid provider keys to frontend code.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Optional watched-wallet Ethereum ingestion can use Etherscan in read-only mode:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(text) Tj T*
(ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=***) Tj T*
(ETHERSCAN_BASE_URL=https://api.etherscan.io/api) Tj T*
(ETHERSCAN_MAX_TRANSACTIONS_PER_WALLET=10) Tj T*
(ETHERSCAN_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=15) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The Etherscan provider only reads watched Ethereum wallet transfers. It does not use) Tj T*
(private keys, sign transactions, trade, or run broad market discovery.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Fallback events are recorded through the model_task_logs foundation. Logs must not store) Tj T*
(prompts, raw responses, API keys or secrets.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(BACKUP AND RESTORE) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Use the backup and restore scripts in /backup.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Stage 0 scripts:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- backup/backup_postgres.sh) Tj T*
(- backup/restore_postgres.sh) Tj T*
(- backup/backup_app_config.sh) Tj T*
(- backup/restore_app_config.sh) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(PostgreSQL backup and restore scripts load .env when present. Backups use custom-format) Tj T*
(pg_dump files and write a .sha256 checksum. Restore verifies the checksum when the) Tj T*
(checksum file is present.) Tj T*
ET
endstream
