(whale_wallets, watchlist, wallet_movements and agent_alerts) Tj T*
(- Ollama is installed locally on 127.0.0.1:11434 and responds with qwen3:4b) Tj T*
(- ChatGPT primary model is configured through environment/provider settings) Tj T*
(- Anthropic fallback is configured through environment/provider settings) Tj T*
(- Mock fallback tests cover token/rate-limit fallback behaviour) Tj T*
(- model_task_logs migration foundation exists for fallback event logging) Tj T*
(- ASVS register exists and records that latest stable ASVS must be checked at audit time) Tj T*
(- No secrets are committed) Tj T*
ET
